# 👤 USER APIs

---

## 1️⃣ Register User

**POST**

```bash
/api/users/register
```

### Body (JSON)

```json
{
  "name": "Aditya",
  "email": "user@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}
```

### Response

```json
{
  "msg": "User Registered Successfully"
}
```

---

## 2️⃣ Login User

**POST**

```bash
/api/users/login
```

### Body

```json
{
  "email": "user@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}
```

### Response

```json
{
  "token": "JWT_TOKEN",
  "user": {
    "id": "USER_ID",
    "name": "Aditya",
    "email": "user@gmail.com"
  }
}
```

⚠️ Save `token` in React (localStorage or context).

